           move      9999999              to   rr-cod-max             .
           move      spaces               to   rr-rag-min             .
           move      all "z"              to   rr-rag-max             .
           move      all "X"              to   rr-vde-stp             .
           move      1                    to   rr-sns-fid             .
           move      1                    to   rr-sns-det             .
       stp-srt-inp-050.
