      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-cli-cod-cli       <    rr-cod-min or
                     rf-cli-cod-cli       >    rr-cod-max or
                     rf-cli-rag-key       <    rr-rag-min or
                     rf-cli-rag-key       >    rr-rag-max
                     go to  stp-srt-inp-200.
